name: A possible landscape 14 (60x84)
description: The possible landscapes are chunks of imaginary topographies made by an algorithm and drawn by a robot. Glitches and imperfections are part of the work. Physical plotter drawing, 60 x 84cm. Signed by the artist. International shipping included (Make sure to verify you H&N profile, DM me your address via twitter). Physical artwork is only guaranteed on the first sale (discuss with owner for secondary market sales).  This file is the vector source file used to create a physcial drawing, and is complementary to https://www.hicetnunc.xyz/objkt/114144 You will also receive an edition of the 114144 OBJKT after purchasing this one. If the original drawing is ever stolen or damaged, it can be recreated with a plotter machine (Axidraw extended is recommended) from the svg.
